pushPlanStep(label)
  → marks previous active completed, appends new step, sets active
startDelegationStep(label)
  → relabels current step if active, else activates next pending, else appends
updatePlanStepDetail(detail | string[])
  → sets detail or detailLines on active step
completePlanStep(ctx)
  → saves substepLines (last 3), marks completed, saves state
errorPlanStep(ctx)
